<Box
  component="form"
  onSubmit={handleSubmit}
  sx={{
    display: "flex",
    gap: 1,
    mb: 1,
    p: 1,
    bgcolor: "#f5f5f5",
    borderRadius: 1,
    alignItems: "center",
  }}
>
  <FormControl sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
    <Input
      type="text"
      value={message}
      onChange={(e) => setMessage(e.target.value)}
      onInput={validateMessage}
      id="message"
      name="message"
      placeholder="Enter your message"
      fullWidth
      sx={{
        bgcolor: "white",
        px: 1,
        py: 0.5,
        borderRadius: 1,
        border: "1px solid #ccc",
      }}
      required
    />
  </FormControl>
  <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit">
    Send
  </Button>
</Box>
